::Prowl::

Prowl looks at Snow Tech as he runs up to him.

"No, I'm fine," he says, "Thanks tough."

He smiles as he sees the newcomers retreating, and growls as a shot digs into 
his shoulder.

"Well, at least they're leaving," Prowl turns to Snow Tech, "Who are you?"
